text: Larysmer Martinez Caro (born 18 October 1996) is a Dominican volleyball player. She played for the Dominican Republic national team at the 2013 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship, the 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, and the 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U23 World Championship. == Clubs == * Deportivo Nacional (2015) == References == == External links == * Larysmer Martinez Caro * VOLLEYBALL • Match players ranking * Dominican Republic’s U23 begins training camp in Japan * VOLLEYBALL • Match result Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Dominican Republic women's volleyball players
